==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Septifragal
<hw>Sep*tif"ra*gal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Septum</ets> + L. <ets>frangere</ets>, <ets>fractum</ets>, to
break.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Breaking from the partitions; --
said of a method of dehiscence in which the valves of a pod break away
from the partitions, and these remain attached to the common
axis.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Septilateral</ent>⟦br⟧
